## Don't

- Don't skip phases or implement Phase 2+ while Phase 1 acceptance is open.
- Don't claim completion without verification command evidence.
- Don't duplicate `hr-research-indonesia` legal content — link and delegate.
- Don't edit `hr-uiux` (read-only reference).
- Don't proceed past a FAIL subagent verdict without user-documented override.
